ps%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2Fwhat-is-certified-foam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECertiPUR-US%20certified%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20they're%20free%20of%20dangerous%20chemicals%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20topper%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oeko-tex.com%2Fen%2Four-standards%2Foeko-tex-standard-100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOeko-Tex%20Certified.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20available%20in%20two%20heights%3A%20two%20inches%20and%20three%20inches.%20The%20two-inch%20version%20is%20typically%20better%20if%20you%20prefer%20a%20medium-firm%20feel%2C%20while%20the%20three-inch%20version%20is%20best%20if%20you%20like%20ultimate%20plushness.%20I%20tested%20the%20two-inch%20version%2C%20while%20home%20and%20sleep%20reviews%20fellow%20Kinsley%20Searltes%20tested%20the%20three-inch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Linenspa%20mattress%20topper%20comes%20in%20a%20plethora%20of%20sizes%20from%20twin%20to%20California%20king%2C%20including%20twin%20XL%2C%20full%20XL%2C%20and%20short%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223571dd9c-20ca-49c8-b5c4-363c1e69f925%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Linenspa%20Mattress%20Topper%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Linenspa%20Mattress%20Topper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20linenspa%20mattress%20topper%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20bed%20frame.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689b63b2194a2d49b8ae695a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Linenspa%20mattress%20topper%20is%20a%20simple%20slab%20of%20memory%20foam%20that%20sits%20directly%20on%20top%20of%20the%20mattress.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20topper%20arrived%20the%20next%20day%20in%20vacuum-sealed%20packaging%20and%20was%20easy%20to%20unroll.%20It%20was%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20carry%20as%20it's