20want%20to%20order%20one.%20Alternatively%2C%20you%20can%20place%20it%20under%20a%20mattress%20pad%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20did.%20Or%20you%20can%20just%20place%20it%20directly%20on%20your%20mattress%20and%20put%20your%20bed%20sheets%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20night%20sleeping%20on%20our%20doctored-up%20bed%20was%20honestly%20pretty%20awesome.%20While%20I%20can't%20say%20it%20was%20like%20sleeping%20on%20a%20cloud%2C%20it%20definitely%20transformed%20our%20hard%20slab%20to%20a%20plusher%2C%20more%20body-conforming%20mattress%20and%20we%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20sleeping%20on%20a%20new%20mattress.%20Searles%20found%20that%20the%20three-inch%20version%20softened%20up%20her%20mattress%2C%20while%20still%20offering%20plenty%20of%20support%20no%20matter%20her%20sleeping%20position.%20She%20recommends%20the%20three-inch%20version%20for%20stomach%20and%20back%20sleepers%2C%20especially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20sleeping%20on%20the%20bed%20for%20several%20weeks%2C%20my%20husband%20noticed%20that%20my%20back%20and%20neck%20pain%20complaints%20subsided%20substantially%20too.%20In%20retrospect%2C%20I%20should%20have%20gone%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151103164573n-20%26h%3D2b066eeb6d9456eb511f98756ebb84fcfc833b38afbf724380d7f028c4f0e1c4%26postID%3D68acbc17a4f74711361822dd%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Flinenspa-memory-foam-mattress-topper-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB07MY1YW3Q%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526tag%253Dbiip_062119_linenspa-mattress-topper-review-20%2526camp%253D1789%2526creative%253D9325%2526linkCode%253Das2%2526creativeASIN%253DB07MY1YW3Q%2526linkId%253Df279d5c06dc01bcc8e2cd06e2a61c119%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree-inch%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20for%20a%20little%20more%20cushioning.%20After%20several%20mont