692790-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIyer%20transformed%20barren%20land%20into%20fertile%20soil%20using%20organic%20matter%20and%20banning%20chemicals%20and%20plastics.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20was%20both%20a%20challenge%20and%20an%20opportunity.%20Some%20sections%20were%20lush%20with%20growth%2C%20while%20others%20lay%20barren.%20His%20first%20task%20was%20to%20transform%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spent%20months%20tending%20to%20it%2C%20nourishing%20it%20with%20organic%20matter%2C%20eliminating%20traces%20of%20past%20chemical%20residues%2C%20and%20restoring%20its%20natural%20balance.%20The%20work%20was%20laborious%20but%20fulfilling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%20immersed%20himself%20in%20the%20science%20of%20organic%20farming%2C%20travelling%20across%20the%20state%20to%20learn%20from%20experts%20and%20experimenting%20with%20innovative%20methods.%20His%20plantation%20became%20his%20classroom.%20He%20nurtured%20the%20land%20until%20it%20became%20a%20fully%20organic%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20any%20chemicals%20or%20plastics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20a%20memorable%20incident%2C%20Iyer%20chuckles%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20received%20a%20call%20from%20my%20head%20gardener.%20His%20voice%20was%20fraught%20with%20panic.%20%E2%80%98Sir%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20invasion!%E2%80%99%20My%20mind%20raced%20%E2%80%94%20a%20locust%20swarm%3F%20A%20mutant%20fungus%3F%20The%20suspense%20was%20unbearable.%20Then%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98There%20are%20worms%2C%20thousands%20of%20them!%E2%80%99%20Worms%3F%20Did%20we%20need%20pest%20control%3F%20But%20he%20explained%20they%20were%20earthworms%2C%20so%20many%20that%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20walk%20without%20stepping%20on%20them!%20I%20burst%20into%20laughter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tiny%20creatures%2C%20far%20from%20being%20pests%2C%20were%20a%20sign%20of%20healthy%20soil%20%E2%80%94%20proof%20that%20his%20organic%20methods%20were%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20soil%20care%2C%20Iyer%20prepares%20his%20own%20cow-dung%20fertilisers%2C%20including%20jeevamrut%20(liquid%20manure%20made%20from%20dung%20and%20urine)%20and%20panchagavya%20(made%20from%20five%20cow-related%20products%3A%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20ghee%2C%20dung%2C%20and%20urine).%20He%20even%20introduces%20music%20therapy%2C%20playing%20calming%20classical%20instrumental%20sounds%20to%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHR-Iyer-Kodaikanal-2-1755692550.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HR%20Iyer%20transformed%2018-acres%20of%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20farm%20of%20coffee%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20cardamom.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHR-Iyer-Kodaikanal-2-1755692550.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHR-Iyer-Kodaikanal-2-1755692550-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHR-Iyer-Kodaikanal-2-1755692550-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHR-Iyer-Kodaikanal-2-1755692550-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHR-Iyer-Kodaikanal-2-1755692550-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489546%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHR%20Iyer%20transformed%2018-acres%20of%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20farm%20of%20coffee%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20cardamom.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E